Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sea of Mist I heard tell of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:12.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that nobody's ever \Ncome back alive from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! This is gonna be a big haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, boss of the tin can, you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to begin aggressive maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideauze colony drawing near.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got overwhelming numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative. Conjecture: On the other hand, \Nin the area of fighting power, I am superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suggestion: Carry out an independent mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing fusillade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll save us some effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I can take \Nout any number of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the Earth-type Hideauze are much \Nweaker than the ones we've encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their combat efficiency is 1/120th of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:33.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With current armaments, it is possible to \Ncontinue attacking and drive them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to massacre \Nthe whole lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.00,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep Sea Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, maintain current \Ncourse. Watch the depth gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sure it's this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get lost in the \Nmiddle of a bunch of whalesquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be cursed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do everything according to \Nplan, there's nothin' to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't panic again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, we're in deep shit here. I've never \Nseen this many whalesquid at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your cool. As long as we \Ndon't agitate them, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking a roundabout \Nroute, towards 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,10 o'clock! Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:20.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Like we thought. A genuine treasure island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did humans really create something \Nas incredible as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check it out. You \Nstay here and keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worrywart. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm inside. There are gigantic \Nmachines around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place isn't just accommodations. \NIt's an industrial facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whalesquid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking lousy spare parts, but \Ngenuine remains of the past civilization!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you've seen enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, the two of us \Ncan't bring it up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do come back, first I\N need to get a rough idea of the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm heading for the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this huge one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! This is a whalesquid nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit! You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinion! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro. I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning: Due to current maximizing, \N23% of my energy has been consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Operating underwater is inefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That's why I've \Ngot the handheld weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing proximity fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell... So they {\i1}can{\i0} be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not demons or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ledo, how you doin' down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Just keep it up. Lure \Nthose bastards out of their nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In another five minutes, \Nwe're gonna be ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning: Density of enemy signs increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number of simultaneous targets is excessive. \NRecommendation: Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready up here! Just say the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-shock barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No damage incurred. Turning off shelter mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Situation report?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, 67% of the enemy's offensive \Ncapability has been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It continues to decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Once you're done there, move \Non to the next spot as per the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's workin' perfectly! Keep tossin' em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, but is that Yunboro gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. That tin can \Nain't your average Yunboro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all those lightbugs! \NThat spray of water was glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though fish can't live \Nhere, there are whalesquid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inference: It appears the enemy force has \Nretreated, likely to defend their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their base... Is that the nest \NPinion was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Echolocation analysis \Ncomplete. Now displaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning: Overall level of \Nfatigue near the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recommendation: Temporarily retreat and \Nthen attack again later at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be a fool to let this chance get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Continuing the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ion concentration rising. \NElectrolysis reaction in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed: Discharge of strong \Nelectromagnetic field in the target range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-shock barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Pinion. Ledo, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ledo! Tin can! What's wrong?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ledo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's keep it goin' here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:53.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down. Still, contrary to \Ntheir looks, they're all pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conjecture: A lack of natural \Nenemies has resulted in devolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can analyze it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much energy do we have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,53%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Ledo and the tin can did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can take all the treasure we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, prepare for landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a thing. The mist is too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the hottie is okay. \NAfter all, Pinion is in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The least he could do is \Nissue a progress report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, all we can do \Nis put our faith in Pinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conjecture: Hideauze in \Nthe process of growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Hideauze children...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:07.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Much is unknown about the Hideauze life \Ncycle. This is valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Hideauze?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Individual organism response analysis \Ncomplete. All patterns match the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth, I will refer \Nto them as Hideauze larvae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A spawning ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conjecture: This facility's \Nadministration block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conjecture: A type of storage medium \Nused in extreme environments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can the data be salvaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Successfully accessed. Now \Nsearching for data standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Approximate standard discovered. \NReasoning engine activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will attempt to restore as well as translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Restoration complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible to disclose data.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This facility is clearly a research \Nfacility from the ancient civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:40.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this material is considered classified\N information by the Galactic Alliance of Humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of that \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is military protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The highest-ranking person on \Nsite has the right to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:56.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the highest-ranking person here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Ledo orders pilot support \Nenlightenment interface system Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to release the classified information!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. The order will be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:32.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty. We need \Nto scout it out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure of your sounding and footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The human race must now start \Nwalking on its own two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the person who has volunteered to take \Nthat first step is right here, Ryan Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dangerous mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:03.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we're backed up by a wonderful \Nstaff, so with their help, this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the fifth ice age almost upon us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the necessity of our research \Nhas reached a critical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, hasty scientific developments \Ndestroy old traditions
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and ruin people's happiness, \Nor so many of you fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, religion and traditions have \Nchanged along with scientific advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of our continuous research, \Nhappiness may be attainable for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take this opportunity to announce \Nthe birth of a free science citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The activities of the Self-evolving \NMovement, nicknamed the Evolvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,are drawing various protests \Nfrom all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:56.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the doubts over \Nhuman genome manipulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which also violates international \Ntreaty provisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Solving the problem that we're up against \Nrequires a more flexible response.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have to say that current \Ninternational regulations are behind the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a response to the increasing problem \Nof the earth's cool-down period,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there are calls for the immediate \Ndevelopment of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now in the Continental Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the development is proceeding apace of \Na space station and interstellar immigration ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:34.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This space development \Ntechnology is essential,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't say that it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, machines aren't going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since last week's shocking \Nleak of inside information,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the worldwide opposition movement \Nagainst the Evolvers has stepped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Continental Union didn't wait \Nfor a United Nations resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,before dispatching a foreign fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, there are a great number of \Ncountries that stand by the Evolvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's expected that the situation \Nwill become even more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the immigrants \Nsearched for a viable planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a search that would take at least \Ndozens, maybe hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one way to \Nsalvage this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:40.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They applied mechanical \Nengineering to biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By evolving the human body, we became \Nable to adapt to the vacuum of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,astronomical distances, \Nand a vast amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The symbiont is a marvelous invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can breathe oxygen underwater and \Nwithstand the water pressure of the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I'm sure it'll adapt \Nto the absolute zero vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets nutrition support from \Nthe symbiotic nanomachines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's similar to photosynthesis, \Nbut is even more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to say bye-bye to Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa is going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll be able...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, the controversial \NEvolvers were under fire again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when their internal information \Nregarding recruiting was leaked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it became clear that a number \Nof atrocious human experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,violating international law had taken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While Earth's sustainable humanosphere is \Nrapidly decreasing due to the cooling trend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the war between the Continental Union and \Nthe Evolvers over escaping Earth is escalating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, the chief battlefields are in \Norbit and at floating launch facilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's thought that the \Nwar will continue to expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've discovered that the Continental Union \Nis working on a large-scale wormhole drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The facility includes a self-destruct system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After completion, they'll simultaneously \Ndestroy it and escape the Solar System,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:41.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,thereby stranding us on Earth, \Nexcept now we know their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By attacking and seizing the \Nwormhole drive for ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we Evolvers will be able to spread the \Ndomain of the living to unknown galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Evolvers will dwell in infinite \Nspace and achieve eternal prosperity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the end of the recorded \Ninformation I could play back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:27.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Several points of contradiction \Nwith official Alliance information are noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its credibility is extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made it and for what purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:40.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypothesis: It is possible the enemy \Ncreated it to manipulate information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy?! What's the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Hideauze \Nwere a lower form of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surviving Hideauze discovered. \NI will destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Set all equipment-related stuff to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Ledo doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:29.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
